<p>The following is a rewrite of my old, very, very bad article, SCP-5555-EX. It was awful. So I gave it a total makeover.</p>
<p>Fun historical fact to tie it all together - Paul Verlaine was a real person who just happened to used the words 'déjà vu' to describe that feeling for the first time.</p>
